# Internal/draft files that must never be part of the public deployment.
# These are not linked from any page nav, but Vercel's static file server
# will happily serve any file present in the deployment output at its exact
# path if it isn't excluded here — file-not-linked is not the same as
# file-not-reachable.
#
# email-audit.html and google-cloud-email-response.html were flagged CRITICAL
# / HIGH by the 2026-07-01 compliance audit: email-audit.html exposes dozens
# of real named third parties' (NIH/NSF/HHS/ARPA-H officials) direct email
# addresses from an internal investor-outreach tracking doc, and
# google-cloud-email-response.html exposes an internal draft business email
# with a real support case number. Neither belongs on a public site.
_internal-team-details.html
email-audit.html
google-cloud-email-response.html
